      • getDataSources

        public PluginDataSource[] getDataSources()
        Returns all data sources from this field can possibly be populated. Each field usually has just one data source. However, because trace files and sample sheets can be imported in arbitrary order, some fields may be populated from either of these data sources. data sources. Note though that we only list the data sources that are actually used by the plugin to set the value of this field.
